    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and presented in truly mint condition, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning driver. From the flawless, deep-gloss finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail reflects a standard of care that is second to none. Fully inspected and mechanically superior, this car delivers a refined driving experience that rivals a brand-new model. Invest in uncompromising quality and enduring value today.",
      "price": 48900.0,
