      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver: a vehicle in pristine, showroom-floor condition. This unit has been maintained with an uncompromising commitment to excellence, featuring an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every detail reflects meticulous care, making this a rare, collector-grade example that stands as a benchmark for its class. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, this is an unrivaled opportunity to secure a vehicle of the highest caliber.",
      "price": 48900.0,
