      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and pampered. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape, practically looking like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you really go hunting for it, but honestly, it\u2019s a total head-turner that drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a pristine ride from someone who truly cares, you\u2019ve found it!",
      "price": 48500.0,
