      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the high-revving S65 V8, showing zero signs of rod bearing wear with recent Blackstone reports to prove it. The DCT logic has been optimized for lightning-fast shifts, and the chassis remains incredibly taut, benefiting from upgraded subframe bushings and a corner-balanced suspension setup that yields surgical turn-in. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a precision instrument with a factory-fresh power band and impeccable thermal management. The paintwork has been treated with a multi-stage correction and ceramic coating to preserve the mirror finish, while the cabin retains that showroom-floor tactile feel. For the driver who demands zero compromise in mechanical integrity and linear power delivery.",
